name: Distress
description:
The moment you realize that life will hurt more than your death. 
While existing, we're forced to become acquainted with sadness. 
There's no antibiotic for the ridding of distress, 
and no alleviation of these intervals of pain we must encounter. 
Behind our eyes, are all these things: our stories, 
our dreams, our deficiencies, and our scars. 
Today would leave a scar"

600 frames, 60 fps, 1080p animated concept art made in Blender.

3 Editions only. 

Contact me on twitter after the purchase, and together with the NFT, 
you will receive a folder with all 600 frames rendered in high definition.
